# Roundabouts vs. Four-Way Stops

Roundabouts might seem trivial, but they're safer and reduce traffic congestion. Four-way stops can be chaotic, leading to more accidents and delays. Let's explore why roundabouts might be the unsung heroes of urban planning and traffic management.
